Package javax.swing.beaninfo.color

Class SwatchSelectionPopup

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.beaninfo.color.SwatchSelectionPopup
  • public class SwatchSelectionPopup
extends java.lang.Object
    An encapsulation of a pop-up window that contains a pair of swatch selection panels (recent and stock colors) and a button used to open the color chooser dialog.
    See Also:
    ColorChooserDialog
